* Iron Raptor looked at Dinobot as she heard Prowl's question, wondering if 
just what he said was true.*

" Hmm...for the CR, yes. I'm betting the only thing can heal him now is his 
own repair system, and it hasn't activated so there's probably something 
wrong with it. And we now have...maybe 6 min to see just what's wrong and 
act on it."

* They reached the CR room doors and the doors slid open, IR spotting the 
repair station and heading off in that direction. She looked back to see if 
Tavatron was following, because she knew that they could really use her help 
with helping Dinobot.
But then she turned her head back towards the station as she came up to it, 
looking over at Prowl, wondering if he was ready to strain his muscles...as 
well as hers, to get this bot up on the table and laying on his back.
There was a lot to do to get Dinobot as right as ever again, but it would be 
a lot in a short amount of time. And there was no room for error.*
